 rpt←showonly types;all;t;x
⍝ Call showactions but restrict the list to only those classes or categories listed in the argument
 all←showactions
 :If ∨/'⍴≢'∊types ⍝ Return a count of available classes and actions
     rpt←0 2⍴0
     rpt⍪←(≢∪all[;1]~⊂'(shared)')'Classes'
     t←'Methods' 'Properties' 'Events'
     x←(t ⎕C⍛⍳all[;2]){⍺,≢⊃,/⍵}⌸(⊂⊂'')~¨⍨,¨all[;3]
     rpt⍪←t,⍨⍪x←x[x[;1]⍳⍳≢t;2]
     rpt⍪←(+/x) 'Total actions'
 :Else
     rpt←all⌿⍨∨/(all[;1 2]~¨⊂'()')∊⍥⎕C(,¨⊆types)~¨⊂'()'
 :EndIf
